The paper deals with a communication network and optimization of information transmission, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The use of energy harvesting and causality constraints suggests a Systems and Control (cs.SY) category. The optimization problem formulation and solution involve mathematical analysis and algorithms, which could be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.MA) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
